# macOS Window Style Demo
# Classic macOS terminal window appearance

Output examples/dvds/macos-style.svg

Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set FontSize 16
Set Title "my-project"
Set Template macos

Type "git status"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "git add ."
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "git commit -m 'Add new feature'"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
